Why fork?

On certain implementations, you get this problem:

http://stackoverflow.com/questions/6128675/image-loading-multiple-times-is-this-a-firefox-ou-a-nivoslider-bug

The plugin works but produces extra requests to the server, something you don't want to happen.

Original:

Nivo Slider is "The Most Awesome jQuery Image Slider". See http://nivo.dev7studios.com for more info.